The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Sports | Liverpool trailing at Fiorentina
                                                   Liverpool trailing at Fiorentina
                      
	Liverpool were trailing 0-2 against Fiorentina at half time in a Group E match of the Champions League at Florence on Tuesday. Stevan Jovetic scored both the goals for the home team. In another match, Lyon were leading 3-0 against Debrecen.         
	In the only completed match of the day, Russian champions FK Rubin Kazan held 10-man Inter Milan 1-1 at home. Alezandro Damian Dominquez scored for the hosts, while Dejan Stankovic equalised for the Italians. Barcelona were leading 1-0 against Dynamo Kiev thanks to a Leo Messi strike, while visitors Arsenal were locked goalless against Olympiakos at half time.                                                                                                                       
